Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:30.98,ep,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無 風 日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你的快遞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 請在這裡簽名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,630)}那個 工作方面缺不缺人手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}他說想找個工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:04:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}哦 你就是大家說的那個宇宙少年嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:04:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}找工作啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}上個月正好有個人退休了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}咦？那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}但是已經雇了新人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}沒事的沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}抓魚的活兒肯定找得到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？ 沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為錯過了洋流交匯帶 最近一直都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:20.18,tips,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,註：暖流與寒流的交匯地帶往往漁業資源豐富
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到忙起來的時候 我會找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在正忙著整理賬單
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這活外行也幹不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋寶呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地點倒是有了眉目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是還要過三天才能到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.43,0:05:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 害你期待了半天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多該去送快遞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我試著自己找看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 很好 很好 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微往上點 往上點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 都說是最上面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 左邊  那邊往左
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 做不來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作的適用條件居然如此嚴格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 數據庫有更新嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍未找到適合貴官從事的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦團的推進裝置正在逐一停止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在那裡傻站著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉換一下心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐 艦團停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒風了啦 沒風
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 集合了 跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這肉夠大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足夠大吃一頓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真虧你搞得到手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.23,0:07:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在搞派對沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易碰到無風日 應該有很多修理工作要做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混到我這個位置 手下幹活的人要多少有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是弗蘭基的船
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.31,0:08:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電源關掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我已經確認過了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 派對會場在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 剛剛那是皮尼歐的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 因為無風日風平浪靜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以會選在這樣的日子裡維修船舶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦團會離開銀河道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電力也會中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只有維修人員才能工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人則全都放假
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝貝爾 你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.87,0:08:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風景不賴吧 這可是絕佳位置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 無風的海面就是這樣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗雅 梅露蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那裡好像不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要游泳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊成！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德也來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別穿那件老土的衣服了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我脫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 身材挺棒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧爾德姆醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就打擾一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是費了好大勁才搞到的好肉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電力還沒恢復啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.80,0:10:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 破廢鐵 你不能想點辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對象焚化完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞啥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:10:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事要交給你去辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去鐵匠婆婆那裡一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你去最合適
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這是只有你才能做到的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你要讓雷德到那種地方去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.92,0:11:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然 誰讓他浪費掉了一盤子的肉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給你了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PartB
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是背後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德他不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡好癢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:11:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,630)}果然癢吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:11:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}這下吃完烤肉又要發胖了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}什麼「又要」啊 梅露蒂你根本不用擔心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}每個人都有自己的標準嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}我完全不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}也有不少男生喜歡肉感的女生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}你還真是天真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誤會這點的話可是要吃苦頭的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還 還是應該運動一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起重機塔的噴水器你知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然電力恢復了 那東西卻沒動靜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.27,0:12:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 又壞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能用衝浪風箏上去開啟水泵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:45.90,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(558,650)}Surf Kite
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 我接下來要參加烤肉派對的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 那麼拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:12:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來比試一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ok 我可不會輸給你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來就不用擔心發胖了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何在積極攝取食物的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又執著於維持體型
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的少女心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本機無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 要怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…破廢鐵 你很黑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 小弟弟你一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這臉蛋長得真甜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好嫩的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終點是起重機塔的頂端
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 升空的方法不要那麼亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詢問採取該行動的必要性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我船上的絞盤你還修不修了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會修的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.55,0:14:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是工作忙得很嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意這些小事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起吃吧 馬上就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 別跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們這裡工作怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉發生了緊急情況
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都叫你別動了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對那傢伙來說也算是有意義的社會實踐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本機表示同意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐 你在那做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼這身打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛在監督船底的檢修
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 這裡的電力什麼時候才會恢復啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作沒法按時完成 可能要停到傍晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒開始嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這身泳衣好大膽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新人不用承擔業績指標的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:15:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事 我到底做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一歸我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定能成為我們店的頭牌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 臀部曲線也很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有活力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體力也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 總是艾米佔甜頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是比賽就是比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一名歸我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛好險呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 你怎麼會在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我接著工作去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順著這條路走就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是場不錯的運動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來就可以放開大吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詢問採取該行動的必要性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.65,0:18:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複 詢問採取該行動的必要性…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:18:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多可以了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕人 你想要這個做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣就能解決的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是某種零件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要回到那裡去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 誰幹的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把派對的事到處提
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.42,0:20:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.51,0:20:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 宇宙少年
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有鹽總覺得不夠味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.91,0:20:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 誰想要？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然婆婆的醬汁最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 不快吃就沒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.87,0:20:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也嚐嚐自己勞動的結晶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 起風了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 幹活去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飽了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.66,0:21:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大概
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 畢竟你是途中才來的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 這場派對明明是為你準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 你沒聽說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為雷德一直沒有找到工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐為了替你打氣才特意安排的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你為大家努力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 為大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.81,0:21:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.99,0:21:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧有你 大家才吃到了美味的烤肉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.31,0:21:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還會陪你一起去找工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.89,0:21:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道雷德哥哥適合什麼工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該還是體力活吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.78,0:21:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.90,0:21:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 皮尼歐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.47,0:22:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你在這種地方偷懶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.35,0:22:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這可是名正言順的工…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.47,0:22:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.33,0:22:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詢問採取該行動的必要性
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.07,0:22:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複 詢問採取該行…

